OL,3,CThousands line the streets for Chinese
OL,4,CNew Year celebrations
OL,6,FChatham Chinese Festival has returned
OL,7,Fto to celebrate the Year of the Horse.
OL,9,FChatham Town Centre has come alive
OL,10,Fwith colour, culture and community
OL,11,Fspirit.
OL,13,FA parade on the High Street attracted
OL,14,Fthousands of spectators with hundreds
OL,15,Fmore taking part in a variety of
OL,16,Flively activities, transforming the
OL,17,Ftown centre into a hub of celebration
OL,18,Fand creativity.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
