OL,3,CThousands line the streets for Chinese
OL,4,CNew Year celebrations
OL,6,FOrganised by Nucleus Arts, Love
OL,7,FChatham, Medway Kut-O Association,
OL,8,FDance Alley and Pentagon Shopping
OL,9,FCentre, the festival celebrates the
OL,10,Fculture and contribution of Medway's
OL,11,FChinese community.
OL,13,FDr David Stokes, CEO of Nucleus Arts
OL,14,Fand Vice Chair of the Chatham Town
OL,15,FForum, said: "The Chatham Chinese
OL,16,FFestival is a powerful celebration of
OL,17,Fcommunity, culture and shared heritage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
