PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772374275
OL,3,CThousands line the streets for Chinese
OL,4,CNew Year celebrations
OL,6,F"Chatham has always been shaped by the
OL,7,Fcontributions of diverse communities
OL,8,Fand this festival gives us an
OL,9,Fopportunity to honour Medway's Chinese
OL,10,Fcommunity, while bringing thousands of
OL,11,Fpeople together in a spirit of joy and
OL,12,Funderstanding.
OL,14,F"We're proud to create free,
OL,15,Faccessible events that make our High
OL,16,FStreet a place of welcome and
OL,17,Fcelebration for everyone."
